<p><strong>月饼邂逅茶</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/d25f3c3712d14172a8a337a97c473074.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">竹林野茶的清雅，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">借着月饼的色彩而明朗，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">月饼的香甜，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">借着富含竹香的茶的清新而消解，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">竹香融入易被人体吸收的茶多酚，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当月饼的甜腻遇上竹林野茶的清香，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清新淡雅，松软不腻，口感相得益彰，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如浓浓的亲情爱意化入心田，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">溶入月光如水的团圆之夜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不经意间，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又温和了脾胃，润择了五脏。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赏月、饮茶、品饼，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让山水印的茶与月，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">伴您花好月圆夜！</p>
